# qBittorrent (Material rewrite) — theme singletons
#
# There is exactly ONE QML module for the whole application: `qBittorrent`.
# These theme singletons belong to that module and are therefore usable by name
# (no local import) from any .qml file in the app. When built via
# qt_add_qml_module the singleton flag is also applied through QT_QML_SINGLETON_TYPE;
# this qmldir keeps the declarations explicit and authoritative.

module qBittorrent

singleton Theme 1.0 Theme.qml
singleton Typography 1.0 Typography.qml
singleton Spacing 1.0 Spacing.qml
singleton Icons 1.0 Icons.qml
singleton StateColors 1.0 StateColors.qml
